viewData.name: PhiLashes Curve Tweezers
viewData.short_description: Tweezers for eyelash extensions used to separate eyelashes. Easy to use for the isolation of natural eyelashes and a great design to catch individual eyelash extensions. The eyelashes are easy to grip and hold.
viewData.long_description: Tweezers for eyelash extensions used to separate eyelashes. Easy to use for the isolation of natural eyelashes and a great design to catch individual eyelash extensions. The eyelashes are easy to grip and hold. Made of high quality stainless steel
